Interface Term

All Known Subinterfaces:

public interface Term

isClosed

boolean isClosed()
Returns true if this term is closed---that is, if it does not have free variables. Hence, this method returns true if and only if getFreeVariables().isEmpty() returns true; however, this method may be faster.

Returns:
